rstood & amp ; was more honest than racist democrats that issue of china could be racialized . the biden negotiated pact between u.k. & amp ; white supremacist settler states of the u.s. & amp ; australia against china is a natural one with its meaning quite clear , if not openly stated . the so-called crisis being played out in the democrat party is a fraud . the progressives who already gave away too much will agree to significantly reduced & amp ; delayed spending on items they say are vital . the real issue for democrats is retaining the `` trump '' tax cuts . by gutting the bbb of its most popular elements , democrats have no language on plight of working class & amp ; have ensured that they will lose one , & amp ; probably both the senate & amp ; house in 2022 . like their radical hanger-ons , the obsession with trump has distorted their vision . support democracy in nicaragua by condemning the election interference of the rogue u.s. state . there is absolutely no difference between the right-wing trump forces & amp ; right-wing neoliberal democrats on issue of u.s. imperialism , except the `` left '' tends to side with democrats . look at the cynical racial politics being played by democrats & amp ; black misleaders on voting rights . the democrats were supposed to come back in january & amp ; pass build back better , instead the new priority is voting rights . in other words , class politics are trumped for identity . supreme court struck down pre-clearence provision of vra in 2013 under your first black president . why did n't democrats do something then ? this is why glen ford called democrats the more effective evil . the trump fox continues to push you into the mouth of democrat wolfs . look at how delicately the liberal press treats the obvious contradictions of the biden administration : `` it 's fair to ask whether the biden administration is beginning to prioritize economics over science , just as democrats once blasted trump for doing . '' https : /